content: Those are some great suggestions, thanks! I'm actually leaning towards trying out Lake Winnebago. I've heard good things about it and it's not too far from me. Do you know if there are any good campgrounds or lodging options nearby? I'd like to make a weekend out of it. By the way, my dog Max, who was with me on the pheasant hunting trip, loves swimming and retrieving, so I was thinking of bringing him along.
